quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Blessed is the One that the kingdom is in His hands, and He is capable of everything"
  67,2,"The One who created the death and the life to test which one of you does better work. And He is the powerful, the forgiving"
  67,3,"The One who created seven skies one above the other. You do not see any inconsistency in the creations of the beneficent. So return the eye (and look again), do you see any cracks"
  67,4,"Then return the eye (and look again and) again, the eye returns to you ashamed and tired"
  67,5,"And We have certainly beautified the world's sky with lamps (stars), and We made them meteorites for (throwing at) the devils, and We prepared the punishment of burning fire for them"
  67,6,"And for those who disbelieved in their Master is punishment of hell, and it is a bad destination"
  67,7,"When they are thrown in it, they hear an awful roar from it while it boils"
  67,8,"It nearly blows up from the rage. Every time a bunch (of disbelievers) is thrown in it, its keepers ask them: did not a warner come to you"
  67,9,"They say: yes, a warner has come to us, but we denied and we said: God did not send down anything, you are only in a great error"
  67,10,"And they (also) say: if we had listened or had understood, we would not be among inhabitants of the burning fire"
  67,11,"So they confess to their sin, and down with the inhabitants of the burning fire"
  67,12,"Those who are afraid of their Master in secret, there is forgiveness and a great reward for them"